#: inc/view/customize/banner/CookiePolicy.php:99
msgctxt "legal-text"
msgid "With this cookie policy, we would like to explain what cookies and cookie-like technologies are, how we and other service provider use them on this website, what information they collect, for how long and for what purposes we use them."
