msgid "This template requires the integration of TCF, as the provider of this template uses this standard. Please activate this in the settings to be able to block this service."
msgstr "Tato šablona vyžaduje integraci TCF, protože poskytovatel této šablony tento standard používá. Abyste mohli tuto službu blokovat, aktivujte ji v nastavení."

#: inc/templates/TemplateConsumers.php:253
